    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/depuy-synthes-vv-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance criteria (QoI difference < 10%, E/uval < 1.96). Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted given the strong quantitative agreement across all QoIs and the regulatory precedent for single-configuration ASTM F1717 testing. The bench test dataset used for validation (vintage 2025-10-31) predates the February 2026 model revision; re-validation with a refreshed dataset is planned for Q2 2026 but is not required to support the current submission given the magnitude of the validation margins.",
